Oh, man, I wish I had 300!

24:41.767 --> 24:43.333
Oh, you don't have it?
No.

24:43.333 --> 24:44.900
Well, I ain't jumping
in for nothin'.

24:44.900 --> 24:46.367
I'll save you.

