to work out, Charlie.

26:59.500 --> 27:01.266
I want everything
to be right.

27:03.200 --> 27:04.600
Well, come here.

27:08.433 --> 27:10.500
Wait.

27:10.500 --> 27:12.400
This is my wedding night.

27:12.400 --> 27:15.200
I want the words.

27:15.200 --> 27:17.967
Come on, say the words.

27:20.667 --> 27:22.967
I love you.

27:22.967 --> 27:24.767
(laughing)

