Two days at
a cut-rate motel.

28:25.700 --> 28:27.567
It was great.

28:27.567 --> 28:29.967
Real uptown stuff.

28:29.967 --> 28:31.533
Pasty didn't like it, huh?

28:31.533 --> 28:33.800
Patsy didn't say a word.
She wouldn't.

28:33.800 --> 28:35.934
I didn't like it,
I didn't like it.

28:35.934 --> 28:38.000
Jesus, you're in a mood.

28:38.000 --> 28:40.467
I've got $12 to my name.

28:40.467 --> 28:42.300
$12 between me and payday.

28:42.300 --> 28:43.900
The money ain't so bad here.

28:43.900 --> 28:45.367
Or so good.

28:45.367 --> 28:47.066
Well, what do you want?

28:47.066 --> 28:49.433
Want to be like that
old fart, Lawrence?

28:49.433 --> 28:51.233
Wear a suit and run the place?

28:51.233 --> 28:53.867
Hell, no.

28:53.867 --> 28:56.333
I'd just like somethin'
different maybe, you know...

28:56.333 --> 28:58.300
Do something a little better.

28:58.300 --> 29:01.500
I'd like to get my
own place maybe.

29:01.500 --> 29:04.266
I don't care,
I ain't gonna do it.

