Now that's not a lie.
You are my friend.

29:20.100 --> 29:22.033
I ain't gonna do it,
so you might as well

29:22.033 --> 29:23.266
quit flapping
your jaws at me.

29:23.266 --> 29:24.433
Oh!

29:24.433 --> 29:25.633
That man from
the show told you

29:25.633 --> 29:27.734
that talent scouts
can't be a relative.

29:29.700 --> 29:32.200
Is that why you give me
that housecoat of yours

29:32.200 --> 29:33.533
