29:33.533 --> 29:36.500
I give you that housecoat
'cause you said you liked it.

29:36.500 --> 29:39.133
Well, I won't
lie on television.

29:39.133 --> 29:42.066
Oh, goddamn it, Mama!
I'm not asking you to lie.

29:42.066 --> 29:44.533
Just don't spill your
guts is all I'm askin'.

29:44.533 --> 29:46.900
Stop that dirty talk now.

29:49.066 --> 29:50.834
Come on, Mama, think
of what it could mean

29:50.834 --> 29:52.900
