national television.

29:52.900 --> 29:55.467
Look it, all you
gotta do is just say,

29:55.467 --> 29:58.934
"Mr. Godfrey,
I'm Hilda Hensley.

29:58.934 --> 30:01.000
"I've brought my friend
Patsy Cline.

30:01.000 --> 30:03.333
I'm her talent scout."

30:03.333 --> 30:05.467
Come on, Mama.

30:05.467 --> 30:06.667
What do I have to do?

30:06.667 --> 30:08.033
Get down on my knees
and beg you?

30:08.033 --> 30:09.500
Oh!
I will, Mama, please?!

30:09.500 --> 30:11.633
Come on, help me
get to be a singer

30:11.633 --> 30:13.667
