31:40.567 --> 31:41.900
Winchester, Virginia.

31:41.900 --> 31:44.700
Oh, that's lovely
country down there.

31:44.700 --> 31:46.667
So, what's Patsy's talent?

31:46.667 --> 31:48.066
She sings.

31:48.066 --> 31:49.934
Does she sing any
better than I do?

31:49.934 --> 31:51.667
Ohh...

31:51.667 --> 31:52.700
Well, she's...

31:52.700 --> 31:54.633
Oh, she's wonderful.

31:54.633 --> 31:56.066
She made a record.

31:56.066 --> 31:57.200
Well, why don't
we bring her out?

31:57.200 --> 32:00.867
Ladies and gentlemen,
let's welcome Patsy Cline.

32:00.867 --> 32:03.066
(music and applause)

32:03.066 --> 32:05.767
Come on, Patsy!
Come on, baby!

